---------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |TOP-N SORT               |                |1       |6           |
|1 |└─HASH RIGHT OUTER JOIN  |                |1       |6           |
|2 |  ├─TABLE FULL SCAN      |setl            |1       |3           |
|3 |  └─SUBPLAN SCAN         |VIEW1           |1       |3           |
|4 |    └─TOP-N SORT         |                |1       |3           |
|5 |      └─HASH GROUP BY    |                |1       |3           |
|6 |        └─TABLE FULL SCAN|dw_drug_ord_detl|1       |3           |
=====================================================================
