|4 |  │   └─HASH GROUP BY    |                |1       |3           |
|5 |  │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN|dw_drug_ord_detl|1       |3           |
|6 |  └─SUBPLAN SCAN         |setl            |1       |3           |
